Description: Basic CRUD Backend with MongoDB as a DataBase for the Book Keeping

End Points:
1) Create Book : http://localhost:4000/api/v1/books/new [POST]
2) Get Book : http://localhost:4000/api/v1/books [GET]
3) Update Book : http://localhost:4000/api/v1/books/:id [PUT]
4) Delete Book : http://localhost:4000/api/v1/books/:id [DELETE]

Followed Model View Controller Approach with comments and clean code and Error Handling.